metadata.name: To see them together
metadata.description:
The mixed media painting (594Ñ…841 mm size) dedicated to St. Valentine's day.  I created it to feel the celebration of love. I hope you as a viewer feel the same. 
NFT includes locked content : 
1. Mediums info I used for this artwork + concept of original painting (the meaning that I laid in this art)
2. Video with painting creation process 45 sec 
3. 3 close up images based on original painting:  
1 jpg - 2097x2097 px 
3 jpg - 1620x2166 px
